      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me, the version of me that actually had dreams and energy, died a long time ago. now i'm just... wandering around in a shell. like i'm a ghost just going through the motions of a life that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
