      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapy feels like trying to fix something that’s already gone. like you’re trying to tune an instrument that’s already been smashed. there’s nothing left to actually repair. it’s not even a feeling anymore, it’s just the reality that the person i was is dead and i’m just the leftovers.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
