    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "kindness doesn't change the fact that the person i was is gone. it's just a way to decorate a tomb. i'm just tired of pretending any of this matters or that there's some future version of me waiting around the corner. everything feels so heavy and pointless, like i'm just taking up space for nothing.",
